textContent:
---sleepover---

Nagka first sleepover na tayo bby!!! Well technically hindi naman first yun, pero first time naten na chill day lang na sleepover! 

I'm so happy na I woke up next to you and I can't wait for the day's na lagi nalang tayong ganon. I love you so much bby!! Ang saya saya ko pag spinospoil kita and I want you to know na I'll happily cook for you, clean for you, driver for you, and love you for the rest of our lives! Naging mas excited ako lalo sa future naten together! Naiimagine ko na rugo yung endless chill days naten together. Naka recliner chair tayo sa sofa tas ako naglalaro tas ikaw naman nagbabasa lang ganern. Tas naka aircon tayo tas ikaw aantukin ka lang hanggang sa makatulog ka na HAHAHAHA my sleepy eepy bby. I love you bby! MWAAA
